&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Are you driven by financial success and rewarding career progression?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Are you motivated by opportunities to continuously self-improve?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Are you someone who could describe yourself as confident, outgoing and ambitious?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are expanding our successful team at Amoria Bond and are looking to speak with ambitious individuals!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A career with us can significantly&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;increase your earnings&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;progress your career&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;through multiple promotions a year and fast track you to achieving your goals...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are Amoria Bond?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amoria Bond is an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;award-winning international recruitment firm&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;providing specialist staffing and consultancy services within the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Engineering, Renewable Energy, IT, and Life Sciences&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;sectors. We&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;operate in over 40 countries&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;and have&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;expanded our offices by over 45%&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Amsterdam, Manchester,&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Cologne, Singapore and Dallas&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;in under 12 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The markets we specialise in are extremely lucrative, high value sectors - meaning a higher earning potential for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will I be doing?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Making&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;business development&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;calls to prospective and existing clients to win projects to work on&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Headhunting candidates&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;to place onto your clients&#39; projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and maintaining relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writing job adverts, building your personal brand and creating social media content to attract top talent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working the full recruitment lifecycle from qualification calls, booking in interviews and delivering offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meeting your clients face-to-face on a regular basis, with&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;current employees travelling across Europe to meet their clients!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do I need?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You live in or around Amsterdam&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You speak German or Dutch and can communicate well in English&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience in sales and communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Above-average motivation, ambition, proactivity and determination&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideally, you have already worked in B2B sales or in similar positions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are open to new challenges and want to utilise your sales experience in a dynamic and exciting industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What&#39;s in it for you?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intensive onboarding by our L&amp;amp;D department&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Structured 10-step progression plan with promotion opportunities from Trainee to Director&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attractive incentives and regular team events such as international sales trips (Dubai, NYC, Skiing), monthly lunch clubs and Early Finish Fridays.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flat hierarchies, open feedback culture and international spirit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attractive earning oppor

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🚀&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Join the Ride: 360° Recruitment Consultant – Amsterdam&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Amoria Bond, part of the Amoria Group)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looking for a young, international environment to launch (or level up) your sales career? Come build something big with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;💼 About Amoria Bond&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re a global recruitment consultancy within the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;IT, Advanced Engineering, and Life Sciences&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;sectors. We’re growing our Amsterdam team with an ambitious&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;360° Recruitment Consultant&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;who thrives in a fast-paced, people-first, high-performance culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🌟 Why You’ll Love It Here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own your success:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Build your own client &amp;amp; candidate portfolio and see direct rewards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supportive, social culture:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;International teammates, after-work socials, monthly incentives, office events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perks on perks:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Uncapped earnings&lt;/strong&gt;, hybrid working options, wellbeing initiatives, and continuous development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clear progression:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;A transparent&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;10-step career pathway&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;from Trainee to Director.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Award-winning training:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We’ll coach you into a sales pro with our L&amp;amp;D program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;💻&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;What You’ll Do (360°)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Win new clients via phone, email, online meetings—and on-site visits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Talent Matchmaking:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Source, qualify, and place top talent across Europe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consulting:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Be the go-to advisor for clients and candidates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Headhunting:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Leverage LinkedIn, job boards, and creative sourcing to find hidden gems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Negotiate &amp;amp; Close:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Drive offers to signature and celebrate the win.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End Support:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Guide candidates through every step of the process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;👀 What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Driven, curious, resilient; excited to learn fast.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Experience in sales/recruitment is great, but not essential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Fluent&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;German or Dutch + English (C1–C2)&lt;/strong&gt;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;or&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;native English&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;plus&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;B2B Sales or Recruitment experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Based in or around&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Amsterdam&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Did we spark your interest? Send your CV and contact details to&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;alanys.dethore@amoriabond.com and I will contact you as soon as I can!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
