&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;umtilg&quot; data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;71&quot;&gt;360 Recruitment Consultant – Engineering &amp;amp; Energy (European Markets)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;73&quot; data-end=&quot;302&quot;&gt;We are expanding our consulting team at Amoria Bond and are looking to speak with experienced Recruitment Consultants who are ready to take ownership of a 360 role within our &lt;strong data-start=&quot;248&quot; data-end=&quot;301&quot;&gt;European Engineering and Renewable Energy markets&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;304&quot; data-end=&quot;626&quot;&gt;This is an opportunity to develop an international desk, working across established and emerging European markets within either Advanced Engineering or Energy. You will be building long-term client relationships, delivering specialist talent solutions, and operating in a highly consultative, high-performance environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;628&quot; data-end=&quot;811&quot;&gt;This role is suited to recruiters who are confident in business development and delivery, and who are motivated by international exposure, market growth, and strong earning potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;628&quot; data-end=&quot;811&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;628&quot; data-end=&quot;811&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;hoele0&quot; data-start=&quot;1772&quot; data-end=&quot;1785&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;838&quot; data-end=&quot;946&quot;&gt;This is a full 360 Recruitment Consultant position focused on developing and growing a European market desk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;948&quot; data-end=&quot;1162&quot;&gt;You will be responsible for building and managing your own client portfolio across Europe, acting as a trusted partner to clients and delivering tailored recruitment solutions within engineering and energy sectors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1164&quot; data-end=&quot;1199&quot;&gt;Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1201&quot; data-end=&quot;1765&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;znlrgq&quot; data-start=&quot;1201&quot; data-end=&quot;1274&quot;&gt;Developing new business across European engineering or energy markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1f82xli&quot; data-start=&quot;1275&quot; data-end=&quot;1342&quot;&gt;Building and maintaining a specialist European client portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1rvmq5v&quot; data-start=&quot;1343&quot; data-end=&quot;1422&quot;&gt;Acting as a consultative partner on cross-border hiring and workforce needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;65crbw&quot; data-start=&quot;1423&quot; data-end=&quot;1483&quot;&gt;Headhunting and engaging specialist technical candidates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;sux6cp&quot; data-start=&quot;1484&quot; data-end=&quot;1559&quot;&gt;Managing the full recruitment lifecycle from brief through to placement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;onb6f&quot; data-start=&quot;1560&quot; data-end=&quot;1622&quot;&gt;Developing and executing your own European market strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;48u63j&quot; data-start=&quot;1623&quot; data-end=&quot;1701&quot;&gt;Building long-term relationships with international clients and candidates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;82gqq0&quot; data-start=&quot;1702&quot; data-end=&quot;1765&quot;&gt;Working across multiple European territories and industries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;hoele0&quot; data-start=&quot;1772&quot; data-end=&quot;1785&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;hoele0&quot; data-start=&quot;1772&quot; data-end=&quot;1785&quot;&gt;About you&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1787&quot; data-end=&quot;1822&quot;&gt;We are looking for individuals who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1824&quot; data-end=&quot;2346&q

&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;fk9gji&quot; data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;64&quot;&gt;360 Recruitment Consultant – Engineering &amp;amp; Energy (UK Market)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;66&quot; data-end=&quot;288&quot;&gt;We are expanding our consulting team at Amoria Bond and are looking to speak with experienced Recruitment Consultants who are ready to take ownership of a 360 role within our &lt;strong data-start=&quot;241&quot; data-end=&quot;287&quot;&gt;UK Engineering and Renewable Energy market&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;290&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;This is an opportunity to join a high-performance environment where you will manage your own desk, build long-term client relationships, and develop a specialist UK market within either Advanced Engineering or Energy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;509&quot; data-end=&quot;742&quot;&gt;The role is suited to recruiters who are confident in both business development and delivery, and who want to progress within a consultative, commercially driven environment with strong earning potential and clear career development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;zn1mh2&quot; data-start=&quot;749&quot; data-end=&quot;767&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;zn1mh2&quot; data-start=&quot;749&quot; data-end=&quot;767&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;769&quot; data-end=&quot;857&quot;&gt;This is a full 360 Recruitment Consultant position focused exclusively on the UK market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;859&quot; data-end=&quot;1065&quot;&gt;You will be responsible for building and growing your own desk, developing long-term partnerships with engineering and energy clients, and delivering high-quality candidates into specialist technical roles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1067&quot; data-end=&quot;1102&quot;&gt;Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1104&quot; data-end=&quot;1647&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;n4bs9&quot; data-start=&quot;1104&quot; data-end=&quot;1174&quot;&gt;Developing new business across the UK Engineering or Energy market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;5juec5&quot; data-start=&quot;1175&quot; data-end=&quot;1226&quot;&gt;Building and managing your own client portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ss9ad9&quot; data-start=&quot;1227&quot; data-end=&quot;1304&quot;&gt;Acting as a consultative partner to clients on workforce and hiring needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1nkeclo&quot; data-start=&quot;1305&quot; data-end=&quot;1376&quot;&gt;Headhunting and engaging specialist candidates in technical markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;120i2vr&quot; data-start=&quot;1377&quot; data-end=&quot;1460&quot;&gt;Managing the full recruitment lifecycle from initial brief through to placement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1oup59a&quot; data-start=&quot;1461&quot; data-end=&quot;1517&quot;&gt;Developing and executing your own UK market strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ocgmud&quot; data-start=&quot;1518&quot; data-end=&quot;1582&quot;&gt;Building long-term relationships with clients and candidates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;med9sw&quot; data-start=&quot;1583&quot; data-end=&quot;1647&quot;&gt;Operating as a trusted advisor within your specialist sector&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;hoele0&quot; data-start=&quot;1654&quot; data-end=&quot;1667&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;hoele0&quot; data-start=&quot;1654&quot; data-end=&quot;1667&quot;&gt;About you&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1669&quot; data-end=&quot;1704&quot;&gt;We are looking for individuals who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1706&quot; data-end=&quot;2211&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1b2d23c&quot; data-start=&quot;1706&quot; data-end=&quot;1787&quot;&gt;Have at least 12 months recruitment experience in a 360 or sales-focused role&lt;/li

&lt;p data-start=&quot;238&quot; data-end=&quot;286&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;238&quot; data-end=&quot;261&quot;&gt;Candidate Consultant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;261&quot; data-end=&quot;264&quot;&gt;Didsbury, Manchester&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;288&quot; data-end=&quot;346&quot;&gt;£27,200 basic | £35–40k OTE Year 1 | £55–70k+ OTE Year 2&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;348&quot; data-end=&quot;454&quot;&gt;Build a high-performance career with structured progression, meaningful impact and real earning potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;456&quot; data-end=&quot;703&quot;&gt;At Amoria Group, we partner with global leaders in tech, engineering and energy industries shaping the future. Our Candidate Consultants play a critical role in connecting talented professionals with opportunities that shape businesses and careers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;705&quot; data-end=&quot;842&quot;&gt;This is an entry-level opportunity with clear progression, structured training and a supportive environment designed to help you succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;844&quot; data-end=&quot;972&quot;&gt;You don’t need prior industry experience. You do need curiosity, organisation and a commitment to delivering a great experience.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;974&quot; data-end=&quot;986&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;974&quot; data-end=&quot;986&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;974&quot; data-end=&quot;986&quot;&gt;As a 180 Consultant, you’ll manage the hiring process end to end, working closely with colleagues and clients to deliver high-quality outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1138&quot; data-end=&quot;1147&quot;&gt;You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1149&quot; data-end=&quot;1526&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1149&quot; data-end=&quot;1217&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1151&quot; data-end=&quot;1217&quot;&gt;Identify and engage talented professionals in specialist markets&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1218&quot; data-end=&quot;1282&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1220&quot; data-end=&quot;1282&quot;&gt;Build trusted relationships with candidates&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1283&quot; data-end=&quot;1344&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1285&quot; data-end=&quot;1344&quot;&gt;Guide candidates through each stage of the hiring journey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1345&quot; data-end=&quot;1397&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1347&quot; data-end=&quot;1397&quot;&gt;Keep processes organised, accurate and compliant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1398&quot; data-end=&quot;1458&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1400&quot; data-end=&quot;1458&quot;&gt;Develop strong market knowledge and commercial awareness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1459&quot; data-end=&quot;1526&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1461&quot; data-end=&quot;1526&quot;&gt;Contribute to a collaborative, high-performing team environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1528&quot; data-end=&quot;1640&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1642&quot; data-end=&quot;1662&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1642&quot; data-end=&quot;1662&quot;&gt;Who Thrives Here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1664&quot; data-end=&quot;1802&quot;&gt;We welcome applicants from a range of backgrounds including customer service, retail, hospitality, call centres or other fast-paced roles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1804&quot; data-end=&quot;1860&quot;&gt;Sales experience can be helpful, but it isn’t essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1862&quot; data-end=&quot;1897&quot;&gt;You’re likely to thrive if you are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;189

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivery Consultant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Didsbury, Manchester&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£27,200 basic | £35–40k OTE Year 1 | £55–70k+ OTE Year 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build a high-performance career in recruitment — with structure, progression and real earning potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Amoria Group&lt;/strong&gt;, we partner with global leaders in tech, engineering and energy — industries shaping the future. Our Delivery Consultants are critical to that success. They drive hiring outcomes, build trusted relationships, and operate with pace, precision and professionalism.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an entry-level role — but not a small one. We’re looking for people who want to grow quickly, take ownership and build a career they’re proud of.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don’t need recruitment experience. You do need focus, drive and a commitment to delivering excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Delivery Consultant, you’ll take ownership of the recruitment process from brief to offer, working in partnership with senior consultants and clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, engage and manage high-calibre candidates in specialist markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver against agreed hiring goals with pace and consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong, credible relationships with candidates and stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain structured, organised processes to ensure quality and compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop deep market knowledge and become a trusted specialist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to team performance and collective success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role rewards discipline, organisation and strong communication. High performance here comes from preparation, attention to detail and consistent follow-through.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome applicants from a range of backgrounds — you might have experience in customer service, retail, hospitality, call centres or another fast-paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sales experience is an advantage, but it is not essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What matters most is that you are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Results-oriented and motivated by achieving goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organised and process-driven&lt;/li&gt;
